WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: 4ILATWjYY_c

NOTE Language: en

00:17:25.677 --> 00:17:39.082
Very happy to see all of you here. Now I can't
say that you are the seekers but you are the

00:17:39.107 --> 00:17:42.427
ones who have found it.

00:17:42.427 --> 00:17:59.382
It's something so fulfilling. Imagine in the
olden days the custom was, I mean, it was

00:17:59.407 --> 00:18:11.291
so, that one guru could give realisation to
one person, with very great reluctance! First

00:18:11.316 --> 00:18:28.352
they had to go through all kinds of tests,
all kinds of tapasya as they call it, very,

00:18:28.377 --> 00:18:42.022
very strict penance. And out of that they
would select one person to get Self-realisation.

00:18:42.047 --> 00:19:00.072
Imagine what you have got in such a short
time! But, with that long period of ordeal,

00:19:00.097 --> 00:19:17.022
they developed a great sense of respecting
their Self-realisation, of understanding what

00:19:17.047 --> 00:19:32.512
is this. Understanding their own powers, understanding
their own duties. And they were not so many.

00:19:32.537 --> 00:19:43.291
One single person fighting the whole society
with his lofty ideas. While today you are

00:19:43.316 --> 00:19:54.942
so many, all of you are in fraternity, in
love with each other. Nobody is going to torture

00:19:54.967 --> 00:20:08.962
you, nobody is going to take you to task,
but you yourself will feel like spreading

00:20:08.987 --> 00:20:19.791
Sahaja Yoga, giving love and life to people.
It will come spontaneously within you. Like

00:20:19.816 --> 00:20:30.852
a flower which has fragrance, like that you'll
have the fragrance of spirituality and people

00:20:30.877 --> 00:20:37.517
will suddenly recognise you because you are
so different from others.

00:20:37.517 --> 00:20:47.872
Your temperament is so different you are so
balanced you are so sweet and they will come

00:20:47.897 --> 00:21:01.012
around, they will follow you. it has happened
very fast in some countries. Like in India

00:21:01.037 --> 00:21:09.161
they know this, they know Self-realisation
and they know that is the aim of life, so

00:21:09.186 --> 00:21:15.457
it was much easier, it has so many Sahaja
yogis.

00:21:15.457 --> 00:21:27.161
But we have sahaja yogis all over the world
now, even in Greenland, can you imagine, in

00:21:27.186 --> 00:21:42.582
Finland in Sweden, in Norway. We have Israelis
and also Palestinians. They are in Sahaja

00:21:42.607 --> 00:21:52.041
Yoga. Supposed to be fighting but both of
them are in Sahaja Yogi. One Israeli telephoned

00:21:52.066 --> 00:22:00.192
to me that 'Mother, there are some Palestinian
sahaja yogis in a village and we have learnt

00:22:00.217 --> 00:22:07.217
that it is going to be bombed. Can you put
your attention to that?' I was so touched.

00:22:07.242 --> 00:22:17.531
Look at the amount of care and love they have
for the so-called enemies! If this kind of

00:22:17.556 --> 00:22:29.212
love grows one day all this wars and skirmishes
all will be finished, there won't be any fights

00:22:29.237 --> 00:22:45.942
if you realise we are all one, just all, absolutely,
in one Divinity, in one Divine Power. If that

00:22:45.967 --> 00:22:54.141
is built in, then all these problems will
be solved about which I told you in my lecture

00:22:54.166 --> 00:22:57.467
(at Royal Albert Hall a few days before).

00:22:57.467 --> 00:23:06.842
Actually Kundalini has risen in many of you,
most of you. It has pierced also the fontanelle

00:23:06.867 --> 00:23:21.492
bone area, no doubt, but still it comes down
sometimes, comes down to cure you. Supposing

00:23:21.517 --> 00:23:31.332
you are a liver patient, the Kundalini will
come down and put full attention to your liver

00:23:31.357 --> 00:23:42.512
and try to improve your liver. She looks after
you. She is your individual Mother. Everyone

00:23:42.537 --> 00:23:52.432
has that Mother within you. And that Mother
is the one that guides you, looks after you

00:23:52.457 --> 00:24:02.421
and takes you to the right path. And that's
how you'll start your new growth in Sahaja

00:24:02.446 --> 00:24:15.741
yoga. You become a different personality.Then
your attention starts moving away from you

00:24:15.766 --> 00:24:28.792
to others. That's the sign you are fully grown.
If that happens that your attention doesn't

00:24:28.817 --> 00:24:36.952
go to yourself, it goes to others and you
are worried about others.

00:24:36.977 --> 00:24:47.542
It's very surprising, how this love of the
Divine works wonders. I had gone to Russia

00:24:47.567 --> 00:24:57.812
first time, and I was surprised, twenty-five
people from Germany and Austria came there

00:24:57.837 --> 00:25:08.832
on there own, I never called them, organised
their stay and everything. And I said 'Why

00:25:08.857 --> 00:25:18.912
are you here? How are you here? How did you
come? What is the speciality of Russia?' And

00:25:18.977 --> 00:25:29.221
they said, 'Mother, our forefathers had done
so much harm to them so we just couldn't help

00:25:29.246 --> 00:25:39.471
it.' It's a kind of a tremendous love and
understanding about the problems of Russians

00:25:39.496 --> 00:25:48.847
during war. And they were telling me what
all had happened to Russians. I was surprised.

00:25:48.872 --> 00:26:02.511
I asked them 'Who told you?' 'Our father,
our grandfather, who were repenting what they

00:26:02.536 --> 00:26:13.127
have done. But they are no more now so we
thought we had better come and do some service.'

00:26:14.966 --> 00:26:23.195
It's very much touching to me. I have seen
such beautiful side of human beings after

00:26:23.285 --> 00:26:37.145
they have got realisation. No cruelty of any
kind, no unkindness, always forgiveness, such

00:26:37.170 --> 00:26:42.246
a lot of people have become now so sweet.

00:26:42.246 --> 00:26:53.812
In Russia we have, as you know, maximum number
of sahaja yogis, not more than India, but

00:26:53.837 --> 00:27:03.498
yes. So many of them are there in Russia,
and they are so deep, so much understanding.

00:27:03.897 --> 00:27:12.193
They never grudge about their problems of
money or anything. They said 'Mother, we have

00:27:12.217 --> 00:27:20.977
only one problem.' 'What problem you have?'
'Of leadership. Give us a nice leader. And

00:27:21.327 --> 00:27:29.441
now,' they said 'we have a nice leader.' He
has accepted Sahaja Yoga, it's a religion

00:27:29.466 --> 00:27:39.991
in Russia. Of course, it is also a religion
in India. But actually it is accepted as an

00:27:40.016 --> 00:27:51.345
official religion in America. Just imagine!

00:27:51.713 --> 00:27:59.702
We think that Americans are so materialistic
and this and that. They are only 200 year

00:27:59.727 --> 00:28:09.929
old nation and how have they grown so deep
into spirituality, how did they realise this,

00:28:12.747 --> 00:28:20.698
that, spirituality is the essence of life.

00:28:20.723 --> 00:28:35.292
Now I am facing you people who are supposed
to be from England and English had these great

00:28:35.317 --> 00:28:44.162
people right from Shakespeare, William Blake,
all of them were realised souls. But what

00:28:44.187 --> 00:28:59.182
I find in their effort is that they are trying
to show so many things for you to understand

00:28:59.207 --> 00:29:08.652
Sahaja Yoga. But what can they do, because
they didn't know how to raise the Kundalini

00:29:08.677 --> 00:29:17.652
perhaps, or the people were absolutely deaf
and dumb that they didn't understand what

00:29:17.677 --> 00:29:23.797
these people tried to convey.

00:29:23.797 --> 00:29:33.236
Most of the poets were realised souls. Most
of the writers were realised souls. How can

00:29:33.297 --> 00:29:46.132
it be that such great people are just lost?
But now when I see you all here I think of

00:29:46.157 --> 00:30:00.307
them. They must be very happy to see you all
enjoying the bliss, the bliss of the Divine.

00:30:01.109 --> 00:30:11.022
There's no end to the description of these
things. You cannot describe it fully. It is

00:30:11.047 --> 00:30:17.266
to be enjoyed. Only thing is, first stage
is thoughtless awareness, which you have to

00:30:17.266 --> 00:30:31.221
achieve. If you have achieved the thoughtless
awareness then you have crossed one step.

00:30:31.246 --> 00:30:36.957
That is the main thing.

00:30:36.957 --> 00:30:48.932
You have to become thoughtlessly aware. It's
not difficult. There's a sanskrit saying that

00:30:48.957 --> 00:31:01.612
you start saying no to every thought. Whatever
thought comes in -- 'Ya neti neti wachane

00:31:01.637 --> 00:31:08.637
nigamor awachus'. Just go on saying 'No. Not
this thought. Not this thought. Not this thought.'

00:31:08.986 --> 00:31:24.312
And you can achieve it. Also raising Kundalini,
forgiving people, you can achieve it. Also

00:31:24.337 --> 00:31:31.702
if you can find out why these thoughts are
coming to you, what is the source of this

00:31:31.727 --> 00:31:42.302
thought. If you could just see what is the
source then you can do it. Suddenly you will

00:31:42.327 --> 00:31:53.272
find you are silent, you are not thinking
but you are aware, fully aware and aware of

00:31:53.297 --> 00:32:04.832
so many things of which you were never aware.
It's something you have to practice, is to

00:32:04.857 --> 00:32:09.486
become thoughtlessly aware.

00:32:09.486 --> 00:32:20.622
This awareness gives a new dimension to your
attention. You develop an attention that works,

00:32:20.647 --> 00:32:33.102
that works. Sitting down here, if you want
to think about something, this attention will

00:32:33.127 --> 00:32:44.102
go and work out the problem. It works out.
You can also do it. But if your attention

00:32:44.127 --> 00:32:52.292
is on small, small things like 'My father
is like this..my sister-in-law is like this'

00:32:52.317 --> 00:33:03.751
all this kind of things, you forget. And don't
condemn yourself either. If you condemn yourself

00:33:03.776 --> 00:33:14.491
it's of no use because now you are a realised
soul. There is no need to condemn but just

00:33:14.516 --> 00:33:24.682
to watch without thinking. That's what is
called as sakshi, is the witness state.

00:33:24.707 --> 00:33:36.672
That witness state you have to attain and
once you attain that witness state you start

00:33:36.697 --> 00:33:48.922
enjoying everything. Supposing somebody is
nasty, you can see the humour behind that.

00:33:48.947 --> 00:33:59.182
Supposing somebody is aggressive, you can
just smile at it. You can see that, poor thing

00:33:59.207 --> 00:34:10.712
you know, he's doing something wrong because
he can't help it, or she is mischievous, doesn't

00:34:10.737 --> 00:34:25.542
matter, she'll be alright. An attitude of
an innocent personality. You are innocent

00:34:25.567 --> 00:34:37.802
you don't see anything wrong with anyone.
If you are cunning you see everybody as cunning.

00:34:37.827 --> 00:34:48.011
But innocence is thousand times blessed by
the Divine. The Divine blesses the innocence.

00:34:48.036 --> 00:34:56.722
Now you might say 'How is it Mother so many
people are killed who were innocent? How it

00:34:56.747 --> 00:35:07.251
has happened?' It's alright, they were not
realised souls, and some of them, like Christ,

00:35:07.276 --> 00:35:16.972
went through through the ordeal. It has a
meaning His crucifixion has a very great meaning.

00:35:16.997 --> 00:35:28.592
For us it is of great help because He crucified
himself. Now we can pass through the Agnya

00:35:28.617 --> 00:35:29.646
chakra.

00:35:29.646 --> 00:35:40.001
Every one have, they all of them have helped
so much in building up your Kundalini, in

00:35:40.026 --> 00:35:51.472
helping you and working it out. All their
so-called ordeals and sacrifices have done

00:35:51.497 --> 00:36:05.741
so much which you will understand through
your witness state. It's all like in a garden,

00:36:05.766 --> 00:36:14.772
everybody has to work, the gardener has to
work, then the seed is put in and the Mother

00:36:14.797 --> 00:36:25.592
Earth has to work and the water has to work
and then it sprouts. Still it takes time,

00:36:25.617 --> 00:36:36.602
then you see when it is a blossom time, all
the flowers are there, but behind those flowers

00:36:36.627 --> 00:36:48.620
there's such a big effort of people. In the
same way, all those people who have put in

00:36:48.656 --> 00:36:55.477
their effort are within us and they will help
us.

00:36:55.477 --> 00:37:02.871
With Sahaja Yoga, getting realisation, if
you don't spread Sahaja Yoga then you have

00:37:02.896 --> 00:37:16.192
done no justice, justice to Sahaja Yoga. You
cannot help it, it's such a thing, just the

00:37:16.217 --> 00:37:26.072
other way round like a man who is selfish.
A selfish man will never like to share but

00:37:26.097 --> 00:37:37.552
a realised soul would like to share everything
with others and enjoy, enjoy the sharing.

00:37:37.577 --> 00:37:46.981
So many beautiful people come up. They become
so beautiful and so nice, so relaxed, so balanced

00:37:47.006 --> 00:37:58.552
that amazing, you are surprised at yourself
that 'I had all this treasure within me? All

00:37:58.577 --> 00:38:11.131
this beauty within me? Which I am absolutely
enjoying.' You enjoy yourself you enjoy others

00:38:11.156 --> 00:38:16.097
you enjoy every little bit of it.

00:38:16.097 --> 00:38:25.312
So I bless you all from my heart. So many
of you got realisation. As I've told you we

00:38:25.337 --> 00:38:32.337
have to change the destiny of human beings.
We have not come here to destroy but we have

00:38:32.896 --> 00:38:41.310
come here to grown and the destiny has to
be changed and that is what we have to work

00:38:41.335 --> 00:38:42.855
out.

00:38:42.880 --> 00:38:45.001
May God bless you.

00:38:55.581 --> 00:39:07.985
Derek Lee: "Shri Mataji there are one or two
new people here" Shri Mataji: "So what do

00:39:08.010 --> 00:39:15.459
they want?" (laughter) Derek Lee: "I don't
know if you want to answer questions or ask

00:39:15.484 --> 00:39:17.245
them to feel..."

00:39:29.230 --> 00:39:34.631
Shri Mataji: (laughing) "Alright! Derek is
trying to look after you all and he says that

00:39:34.656 --> 00:39:41.656
there are many new people here and they would
like to ask you questions. (laughter) So you

00:39:51.124 --> 00:40:02.341
see sometimes I'm surprised because you become
just like a criminal or you have to confess

00:40:02.366 --> 00:40:13.193
something. Like yesterday they asked me 'Are
you a Goddess?' I said 'Bapare, what should

00:40:13.218 --> 00:40:21.881
I say?' I said 'Do you want me to confess
something?' Then they kept quiet. So now what's

00:40:21.906 --> 00:40:30.511
all the questions. Questions should be related
to your growth and not to nonsensical things,

00:40:30.536 --> 00:40:41.282
why waste energy? It's not a political party
or anything, it's something spiritual. So

00:40:41.307 --> 00:40:48.307
if you want to ask, ask for your spiritual
growth."

